 full recovery. She has understandably been left deeply upset by this horrendous ordeal.</p><p>\"This type of senseless violence will not be tolerated and I would urge anyone who may have seen or heard anything out of the ordinary in St George's Hill late on Friday night into the early hours of Saturday morning to call police as a matter of urgency.\"</p><p>Anyone who witnessed the burglary or has any information should call Surrey police on 101 or Crimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555111.</p>","headline":"Woman tortured during burglary tells of waterboarding ordeal","trailText":"<p>Francoise Jansen, 73, suffered multiple injuries during robbery at Surrey home in which raiders doused her with boiling water</p>","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"theguardian.com","showInRelatedContent":"true","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/39heg","wordcount":"502","commentable":"false","internalContentCode":"394290213","allowUgc":"false","internalOctopusCode":"6513132","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Press Association","internalPageCode":"1784257","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2012-08-10T08:56:39Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/aug/07/woman-torture-burglary-waterboard-surrey","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk/2012/aug/07/woman-torture-burglary-waterboard-surrey","tags":[{"id":"uk/ukcrime","webTitle":"Crime","type":"keyword","sectionId":"uk-news","sectionName":"UK news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk/ukcrime","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk/ukcrime","references":[]},{"id":"uk/uk","webTitle":"UK news","type":"keyword","sectionId":"uk-news","sectionName":"UK news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk/uk","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk/uk","references":[]},{"id":"tone/news","webTitle":"News","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/news","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/tone/news","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Ar